Use query faceting settings to control whether filters get applied to embedded dashboards. 
To apply filters to a dashboard when it’s opened from a link widget, enable faceting in the underlying query. 
Filters aren’t applied to embedded dashboards when faceting in underlying queries is set to Include, Exclude, or None.
